com.vmware.vapi.provider.local

Class LocalProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.vapi.provider.local.LocalProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ApiProvider, SyncApiIntrospection

    public class LocalProvider
extends Object
implements ApiProvider, SyncApiIntrospection
    The LocalProvider class is a local (in-process) implementation of the ApiProvider interface.

    Thread-safety: This class is thread-safe.

      • LocalProvider

        public LocalProvider(String name,
                     List<ApiInterface> ifaces,
                     boolean deployIntrospectionServices)
        Constructor. Optionally can deploy a set of introspection services which expose the introspection API of the provider through invoke(String, String, DataValue, ExecutionContext, AsyncHandle).
        Parameters:
        name - name of the provider
        ifaces - list of ApiInterfaces to register with this provider
        deployIntrospectionServices - whether to automatically deploy introspection services
